title: #92Noon! Montage/JG/Birk&Siny/Bercich/PJ
description: The loss in Tampa starts 92Noon, followed by JG on the Gophers, then Matt Birk & Dave Sinykin round out the first hour....Bercich joins for two segments of Vikings analysis, more NFL talkers throughout, leading to PJ Fleck's weekly appearance to end the show!
